        section#privacyPage 
            div#privacy-intro  
                li.privacy-notice 
                    h1 Privacy Notice 
                li.date
                    p Last Modified: May 5, 2023
                li.intro-part1 
                    p Welcome to BeautyZenith ("us," "we," or "our"). We value your trust and are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you visit and use our website to purchase and import cosmetic products from China.
                li.intro-part2 
                    p By accessing or using our website, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our practices, please do not use our website.

            #info-we-collect 
                li.info-heading 
                    h4 Information We Collect 
                li.info1 
                    p 
                       strong Personal Information: 
                       | When you make a purchase on our website, we collect information such as your Name, Billing and Shipping Addresses, E-mail Address, Phone Number, and Payment Information.
                li.info2 
                    p 
                        strong Browsing Information: 
                        | We collect non-personal information as well, including your IP address, browser type, device information, and pages visited on our website. This information helps us enhance your browsing experience and improve our services.
            
            #info-usage 
                li.info-usage-heading 
                    h4 How We Use Your Information 
                li.info-usage1 
                    p 
                        strong Order Processing and Customer Service: 
                        | We use your personal information to process your orders, fulfill your purchases and provide customer support related to your orders.
                li.info-usage2 
                    p 
                        strong Communication: 
                        | We may use your email address to send order confirmations, shipping updates, and other transaction-related communications. We may also send you marketing emails if you opt-in to receive them.
                li.info-usage3 
                    p 
                        strong Improvement of Services: 
                        | We analyze browsing information to understand how users interact with our website, identify areas for improvement, and optimize our website's performance and user experience.
                li.info-usage4 
                    p 
                        strong Legal Obligations: 
                        | We may disclose your personal information to comply with legal obligations, respond to government requests, or protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property, as permitted by law.
            
            #data-security 
                li.security-heading 
                    h4 Data Security Policy
                li.security-info 
                    p We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            
            #cookies 
                li.cookies-heading 
                    h4 Cookies and Tracking Technologies
                li.cookies-info 
                    p We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze usage patterns, and improve our website's functionality. You can modify your browser settings to control cookies or opt-out of certain tracking technologies.

            #third-party-services 
                li.services-heading 
                    h4 Third-Party Services
                li.services-info 
                    p We may use third-party services that collect, monitor, and analyze information to improve our services. These third-party service providers have their own privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing them.

            #children-policy
                li.policy-heading 
                    h4 Children's Privacy
                li.policy-info 
                    p Our website is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 16. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to remove that information from our systems.
            #policy-changes 
                li.changes-heading 
                    h4 Changes to Privacy Policy
                li.changes-info 
                    p We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy. Changes are effective upon posting, so we recommend reviewing this Privacy Policy periodically.
            #contact-details 
                li.contact-heading 
                    h4 Contact Us
                li.contact-info 
                    p If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to your personal information or this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [contact email or form].
            #end 
                li.end-line 
                    p Thank you for trusting BeautyZenith with your Cosmetic Product purchases.


